====Definitions====
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to [[omit]]; to [[leave out]]
# to [[reduce]]; to [[simplify]]
#* {{zh-x|船：舟 也。从 舟，鉛 省{shěng} 聲。|{{l|zh|船}}: boat. From {{l|zh|舟}}, and a reduced form of {{l|zh|鉛}} used as the phonetic component.|ref=Shuowen}}
# {{lb|zh|colloquial|by extension}} to have less strange, potentially genius but generally lousy ideas for the sake of others to save worry
#: {{zh-x|你 還是 省{shěng} 省{shěng} 吧。|You'd better give it up.}}
# to [[save]]; to [[economize]]
